Dominic Solanke and Everton&rsquo;s Ademola Lookman are being &ldquo;allowed to decide&rdquo; whether they want to switch their international allegiance to Nigeria.<br />
<br />
&ldquo;Ademola Lookman and Solanke are not convinced. They have not made up their minds so we will allow them to decide. We will go back to them later, but we cannot force anybody to play for us. It is very important decisions for them to make.&rdquo;
